m>, you build your realm, one card at a time, as you collect heroes, quests, monsters, and more! Each card is unique, and scores points based on the other cards in your hand. You start with seven cards, and each turn, you draw a new card from the deck or discard area, then discard one card from your hand, always trying to improve your realm. Whoever's realm scores the most points wins.</p>\n\n<p><em>Fantasy Realms: Greek Legends</em> takes the classic <em>Fantasy Realms</em> formula and adds new twists to match its theme. In addition to combining the right suits and attribute tags, you will:</p>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>Send cards to the afterlife, costing precious points but unlocking powerful abilities</li>\n    <li>Complete quests with unique card combinations</li>\n    <li>Vanquish legendary monsters with the right heroes</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><em>-description from designer</em></p>\n\n","wiki":"<span class='text-muted'>This page does not exist. You can edit this page to create it.</span>","website":{"url":false},"imageid":"8428299","images":{"thumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/sz9h3Hb8uSDh1SMocGXmWA__small/img/qYV56vqGKZGWIcdbalkg-HvBfIQ=/fit-in/200x150/filters:strip_icc()/pic8428299.jpg","micro":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/sz9h3Hb8uSDh1SMocGXmWA__micro/img/paVbJfWVq7wZ73tQ2kWEQe4iCWE=/fit-in/64x64/filters:strip_icc()/pic8428299.jpg","square":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/sz9h3Hb8uSDh1SMocGXmWA__square/img/scWCqPjs4ZrPLHFnD_FRHyrzSdg=/75x75/filters:strip_icc()/pic8428299.jpg","tallthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/sz9h3Hb8uSDh1SMocGXmWA__tallthumb/img/pwJNoylPNeUDzE8sL6KGqZElrFk=/fit-in/75x125/filters:strip_icc()/pic8428299.jpg","previewthumb":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/sz9h3Hb8uSDh1SMocGXmWA__previewthumb/img/Qvn8q-2zIpXhQgJI9va9Z8_fu6o=/fit-in/300x320/filters:strip_icc()/pic8428299.jpg","square200":"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/sz9h3Hb8uSDh1SMocGXmWA__square200/img/-eTbhRZSIIvUA8Qz56Rh74DweQg=/200x200/filters:strip_icc()/pic8428299.jpg","original":"https://cf.g